#: ../../../blog/posts/2025-05-28-python-poe-to-doit-migration.rst:8
msgid "Python開発環境での poethepoet → doit への移行とベストプラクティス"
msgstr ""
"Migrating from poethepoet to doit in a Python development environment and "
"best practices"

#: ../../../blog/posts/2025-05-28-python-poe-to-doit-migration.rst:10
msgid ""
"Poetry を使った Python プロジェクトで、これまで `poethepoet` を使ってタスク管理をしていたが、以下の理由から `doit` "
"への移行を行った。"
msgstr ""
"In my Python project using Poetry, I used `poethepoet` to manage tasks, but "
"I decided to migrate to `doit` for the following reasons."

#: ../../../blog/posts/2025-05-28-python-poe-to-doit-migration.rst:12
msgid "より柔軟な依存関係管理とカスタマイズが可能"
msgstr "Allows for more flexible dependency management and customization"

#: ../../../blog/posts/2025-05-28-python-poe-to-doit-migration.rst:13
msgid "複数タスクの依存や並列実行への対応が容易"
msgstr "Easily supports multiple task dependencies and parallel execution"

#: ../../../blog/posts/2025-05-28-python-poe-to-doit-migration.rst:14
msgid "Sphinx 多言語ビルドや静的ファイルコピーなどを整理したかった"
msgstr ""
"I wanted to organize Sphinx multilingual builds, static file copies, etc."

#: ../../../blog/posts/2025-05-28-python-poe-to-doit-migration.rst:15
msgid "`setup.py` に書いていたカスタムコマンドを `dodo.py` に統合したかった"
msgstr ""
"I wanted to integrate the custom commands written in `setup.py` into "
"`dodo.py`"

#: ../../../blog/posts/2025-05-28-python-poe-to-doit-migration.rst:22
msgid "背景と現状"
msgstr "Background and current situation"

#: ../../../blog/posts/2025-05-28-python-poe-to-doit-migration.rst:24
msgid "従来の構成では以下のような形でタスクを管理していた："
msgstr ""
"In the traditional configuration, tasks were managed in the following way:"

#: ../../../blog/posts/2025-05-28-python-poe-to-doit-migration.rst:26
msgid "`poetry run poe doc` → `python setup.py doc`"
msgstr "`poetry run poe doc` → `python setup.py doc`"

#: ../../../blog/posts/2025-05-28-python-poe-to-doit-migration.rst:27
msgid "`poetry run poe gettext` → `python setup.py gettext`"
msgstr "`poetry run poe gettext` → `python setup.py gettext`"

#: ../../../blog/posts/2025-05-28-python-poe-to-doit-migration.rst:28
msgid "`setup.py` に `doc` / `gettext` コマンドクラスを定義"
msgstr "Define `doc` / `gettext` command class in `setup.py`"

#: ../../../blog/posts/2025-05-28-python-poe-to-doit-migration.rst:29
msgid "pyproject.toml の `[tool.poe.tasks]` でラップ"
msgstr "Wrapped in `[tool.poe.tasks]` in pyproject.toml"

#: ../../../blog/posts/2025-05-28-python-poe-to-doit-migration.rst:31
msgid "この構成は、ある程度うまく動作していたが、次のような課題もあった："
msgstr ""
"Although this configuration worked reasonably well, it also had the "
"following challenges:"

#: ../../../blog/posts/2025-05-28-python-poe-to-doit-migration.rst:33
msgid "`setup.py` に依存してしまう点（非推奨方向）"
msgstr "Depends on `setup.py` (not recommended)"

#: ../../../blog/posts/2025-05-28-python-poe-to-doit-migration.rst:34
msgid "タスクの柔軟な定義（ファイル依存・再実行判定）には限界"
msgstr ""
"There are limits to flexible task definition (file dependence/re-execution "
"determination)"

#: ../../../blog/posts/2025-05-28-python-poe-to-doit-migration.rst:35
msgid "`pre-commit` の導入との併用が中途半端"
msgstr "Cannot be used in conjunction with the introduction of `pre-commit`"

#: ../../../blog/posts/2025-05-28-python-poe-to-doit-migration.rst:38
msgid "doit への移行ステップ"
msgstr "Steps to transition to doit"

#: ../../../blog/posts/2025-05-28-python-poe-to-doit-migration.rst:40
msgid "まず `doit` を開発依存として追加："
msgstr "First add `doit` as a development dependency:"

#: ../../../blog/posts/2025-05-28-python-poe-to-doit-migration.rst:46
msgid "プロジェクトルートに `dodo.py` を作成し、以下のようにタスクを定義："
msgstr "Create `dodo.py` in the project root and define the task as below:"

#: ../../../blog/posts/2025-05-28-python-poe-to-doit-migration.rst:64
msgid "動作確認："
msgstr "Operation confirmation:"

#: ../../../blog/posts/2025-05-28-python-poe-to-doit-migration.rst:71
msgid "問題なければ `poe` を削除："
msgstr "If there is no problem, delete `poe`:"

#: ../../../blog/posts/2025-05-28-python-poe-to-doit-migration.rst:77
msgid "併せて `[tool.poe.tasks]` セクションも `pyproject.toml` から削除。"
msgstr "Also, delete the `[tool.poe.tasks]` section from `pyproject.toml`."

#: ../../../blog/posts/2025-05-28-python-poe-to-doit-migration.rst:79
msgid "`.doit.db.db` は Git 管理対象外とするため、`.gitignore` に以下を追加："
msgstr ""
"Since `.doit.db.db` is not managed by Git, add the following to "
"`.gitignore`:"

#: ../../../blog/posts/2025-05-28-python-poe-to-doit-migration.rst:86
msgid "pre-commit の併用"
msgstr "Use with pre-commit"

#: ../../../blog/posts/2025-05-28-python-poe-to-doit-migration.rst:88
msgid "コードフォーマットや静的解析は `pre-commit` で行うように変更。"
msgstr "Changed code format and static analysis to be done in `pre-commit`."

#: ../../../blog/posts/2025-05-28-python-poe-to-doit-migration.rst:107
msgid "利点まとめ"
msgstr "Summary of advantages"

#: ../../../blog/posts/2025-05-28-python-poe-to-doit-migration.rst:109
msgid "`doit` は Python ベースで拡張性が高く、再実行判定も優秀"
msgstr ""
"`doit` is based on Python, has high extensibility, and has excellent re-"
"execution judgment."

#: ../../../blog/posts/2025-05-28-python-poe-to-doit-migration.rst:110
msgid "`setup.py` を廃止し、 `pyproject.toml` 中心の構成へ整理できた"
msgstr ""
"`setup.py` was abolished and the structure was organized around "
"`pyproject.toml`"

#: ../../../blog/posts/2025-05-28-python-poe-to-doit-migration.rst:111
msgid "`pre-commit` によってコミット前のチェックも統一的に管理"
msgstr "Uniformly manage pre-commit checks with `pre-commit`"

#: ../../../blog/posts/2025-05-28-python-poe-to-doit-migration.rst:112
msgid "タスクの実行結果キャッシュも `.doit.db.db` により最適化"
msgstr "Task execution result cache is also optimized using `.doit.db.db`"

